NOTICE — Ported i18n Data and Loader

This directory contains language data files and a minimal loader originally
created by the MemPalace project and used under the MIT License.

  Source repository: https://github.com/MemPalace/mempalace
  Source commit:     65fa1517a1ebd921d346812b0322dce9a39519df
  Copyright:         2026 MemPalace Contributors

The JSON files under this directory are verbatim copies of the corresponding
files in `mempalace/i18n/`. The `__init__.py` loader is a minimal adaptation of
`mempalace/i18n/__init__.py`, keeping only the entity-pattern loading helpers
used for cross-language cue extraction.

